==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɜː(r)ʃə|-ɜː(r)ʃə]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# {{physics}} The property of a [[body]] that [[resist]]s any [[change]] to its uniform straight [[motion]]; equivalent to its [[mass]].
# (''figurative'') In a person, [[unwilling]]ness to take [[action]].

====Synonyms====
*(''unwillingness to take action''): [[idleness]], [[laziness]], [[sloth]], [[slothfulness]]

